imdb.plot outline: The world has become obsessed with the everyday lives of celebrities from the A list to the Z list, but behind the scenes managers and publicists are controlling, manipulating and protecting their celebrity clients. MTV One gain full access to one of the leading celebrity management and PR companies in the UK, Jonathan Lipman International Group (JLIG) open up the doors to show the exciting industry of how it all happens behind the scenes. We follow key figure's within the company doing what they do best. the camera's follow Jonathan Lipman and his staff Stephen Naylor and Carly Bauckham, plus a new member joins the team, but who??
